0) stop all running scripts
  - spamd
  - smtpd
  - dovecot
  - rspamd

1) cp -a /etc/ansimail /etc/excision
  1.1) in the dkim and dkim/private folder
       rename all files of the form
       ansimail.domain.tld.*  ->  excision.domain.tld.*
  1.2) in the nsd folder
       for each zone file "domain.tld.zone"
       replace ANSIMAILSERIAL by EXCISIONSERIAL
  1.3) in the ssl folder
       correct the domain key and full chain certificate paths
       change ansimail -> excision

2) rename the ansimail group to excision
   groupmod -n excision ansimail

3) rename the ansimail user to excision while also moving
   the home directory
   usermod -m -d /var/excision-home -l excision ansimail

4) rename the ansimail-passwd user to excision-passwd while
   also moving the home directory
   usermod -m -d /var/excision-passwd -l excision-passwd ansimail-passwd

5) mv /var/ansimail /var/excision

   